♪A thousand candles light up the hall♪

180
00:09:48,540 --> 00:09:53,340
♪I long to chat among flowers
beneath the moon♪

181
00:09:53,340 --> 00:09:56,180
♪Wine is quick to intoxicate,
and cups to break♪

182
